  "title": "Sous Chef",
  "description": "<p>•Follow recipes, portion controls, and presentation specifications as set by the Company. </p><p>•Ensure that all areas of the kitchen are clean and sanitized including kitchen equipment and utensils. </p><p>•Ensure that all food is processed according to the corporate and government regulator control in hygiene and sanitation standards. </p><p>•Ensure the safe operation of all cleaning equipment and report any faulty equipment to the Head. </p><p>•Assist in planning of menus and recipes with the Head Chef and/ or Executive Chef. </p><p>•Strictly adhere to minimize food and supply waste and theft. </p><p>•Performs any other duties as directed by the Head Chef and / or Executive Chef. </p><p>•Any other ad-hoc tasks assigned from time to time.    </p>",
